OL,3,CPair charged with 'malicious mischief'
OL,4,Cat Trump golf course
OL,6,FTwo people have appeared in court
OL,7,Fcharged over vandalism at Donald
OL,8,FTrump's golf course in Scotland.
OL,10,FRicky Southall, 33, of Wakefield, and
OL,11,F55-year-old Umza Bashir, of Leeds,
OL,12,Fwere charged with malicious mischief
OL,13,Fwhen they appeared in private at Ayr
OL,14,FSheriff Court on Monday.
OL,16,FRed paint was sprayed on the clubhouse
OL,17,Fand the greens were damaged in an
OL,18,Fincident at the Trump Turnberry course
OL,19,Fin South Ayrshire on 8 March.
