OL,4,Cat Trump golf course
OL,6,FKieran Robson, 33, of Galashiels in
OL,7,Fthe Scottish Borders, made no plea
OL,8,Fduring the brief hearing and was
OL,9,Fcommitted for further examination and
OL,10,Freleased on bail pending a further
OL,11,Fcourt appearance.
OL,13,FA Scottish Government publication from
OL,14,FOctober 2023 defines the common law
OL,15,Foffence of malicious mischief as the
OL,16,Fwilful, wanton and malicious
OL,17,Fdestruction of, or damage to, the
OL,18,Fproperty of another.
